{"type":"message","id":"66edc2e3","parentId":"07e08539","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:09:07.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在需要每天八点发浙江台州临海的今明后三天天气预报，首先我要匹配技能，看available_skills里有weather的skill对吧，还有效率自动化工具箱？不对，首先这个是定时提醒加天气预报，首先需要实现定时任务，还有调用天气接口对吧？首先，先看weather skill的说明，是用wttr.in或者Open-Meteo，不需要API key，然后还要设置定时任务对吧？还有productivity-automation-kit那个技能，触发词有每天提醒，对吧？不对，先理清楚步骤：\n首先，我需要先读weather的SKILL.md，了解怎么获取天气预报，然后读productivity-automation-kit的SKILL.md？不对，用户的需求是每天八点定时发送，所以首先要配置定时任务，然后写个脚本获取天气预报，然后发送到这个飞书群对吧？\n不对，先第一步，先调用read工具读weather的skill文件，先搞清楚怎么获取天气。哦对了，技能里的weather的location是~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md对吧？先读这个。\n等下，还有，用户要的是每天八点发送，所以需要设置cron任务对吧？还有发送到飞书群，所以还要知道怎么发飞书消息？哦对了，飞书相关的技能，但用户现在的需求是天气预报加定时发送，先先读weather的skill吧。\n所以第一步调用read工具，读取weather的SKILL.md文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_57cfl9l310x0h8xb5sp7bclb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775729338638,"responseId":"021775729338556d323cdad39964ab14a5fcc08ad1c3650471d10"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce2a3808","parentId":"66edc2e3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:09:07.270Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_57cfl9l310x0h8xb5sp7bclb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"☔\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"curl\",\n              \"bins\": [\"curl\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install curl (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775729347261}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f95daf4","parentId":"ce2a3808","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:09:20.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n现在我已经知道怎么获取天气预报了，接下来需要设置每天8点定时发送到这个飞书群的任务。首先我需要创建一个定时任务脚本，然后配置cron定时执行，还要能发送消息到当前飞书群对吧？首先先写一个获取台州临海3天天气预报的脚本，然后配置cron任务，每天8点运行，然后把结果发送到飞书群。\n首先，先写一个shell脚本，路径就放在工作区的scripts目录下吧，比如weather_report.sh。首先脚本内容应该是：\n1. 获取浙江台州临海的3天天气预报\n2. 把结果发送到当前飞书群\n哦对了，怎么发送飞书群消息？哦我现在可以直接在这个群回复，不过定时任务的话需要用飞书的webhook？或者用openclaw的sessions_send工具？对，sessions_send可以发送消息到指定session，当前的sessionKey是chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575对吧？\n不对，先确认下，当前的chat_id是chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575，所以sessions_send的sessionKey就是这个值对吧。\n那脚本内容大概是：\n#!/bin/bash\n# 获取浙江台州临海3天天气预报\nforecast=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/浙江台州临海?0?1?2?format=%l\\n%c+%t+%p+%w\\n明天：%c+%t+%p+%w\\n后天：%c+%t+%p+%w\")\n# 发送到飞书群\nopenclaw sessions send --session-key \"chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\" --message \"📅 台州临海今明后三天天气预报：\\n$forecast\"\n然后给脚本加执行权限，然后添加cron任务，每天8点执行：0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh >> /var/log/weather_report.log 2>&1\n不对，先创建scripts目录，然后写这个脚本对吧。首先调用write工具写这个脚本。\n首先路径是/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh，内容就是上面的脚本。\n然后接下来要设置cron任务，还要给脚本加执行权限。\n等下，先写脚本吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wbzs65mc7u24fs4b3dc3i3ke","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 台州临海今明后三天天气预报定时发送脚本\nforecast=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/浙江台州临海?format=%l\\n\\n🌤️ 今日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\\n🌤️ 明日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\\n🌤️ 后日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\")\n\n# 发送到当前飞书群\nopenclaw sessions send --session-key \"chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\" --message \"📅 台州临海天气预报提醒：\n$forecast\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason"