{"type":"message","id":"bbbe59c8","parentId":"37d86f7b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:09:26.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n现在脚本写好了，接下来需要给脚本加执行权限，然后添加cron定时任务，每天早上8点执行。首先用exec命令给脚本加执行权限，然后添加cron任务。\n首先执行chmod +x /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh，然后添加cron条目：0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/weather_report.log 2>&1，还要先创建logs目录对吧？\n对，先创建logs目录，然后加执行权限，然后添加cron任务。\n首先执行mkdir -p /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs，然后chmod +x那个脚本，然后用crontab -e添加任务？不对，用echo命令添加到crontab吧，比如：(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/weather_report.log 2>&1\") | crontab -\n这样就能添加cron任务了。\n所以现在调用exec工具执行这些命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aieq43i9560uem4o83xutawx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs && chmod +x /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh && (crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/weather_report.log 2>&1\") | crontab -"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775729360790,"responseId":"021775729359279d323cdad39964ab14a5fcc08ad1c3650a536b7"}}
