{"type":"message","id":"167594a0","parentId":"66558663","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:04:20.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n太好了，天气接口是正常的，就是之前用中文加format参数的时候编码有问题。那我现在修改脚本，用Linhai来查询，并且调整下format参数，或者直接获取3天的格式化内容，然后发送。首先编辑weather_report.sh脚本，把查询地址改成Linhai，去掉有问题的format参数，直接用简化的格式，或者用3天的查询结果，然后处理成文本发送。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ghir8ahmfdcyphuqz83urqjc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"#!/bin/bash\n# 台州临海今明后三天天气预报定时发送脚本\nforecast=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/浙江台州临海?format=%l\\n\\n🌤️ 今日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\\n🌤️ 明日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\\n🌤️ 后日：%c %t 降水概率%p 风力%w\")\n\n# 发送到当前飞书群\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw sessions send --session-key \"chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\" --message \"📅 台州临海天气预报提醒：\n$forecast\"","newText":"#!/bin/bash\n# 台州临海今明后三天天气预报定时发送脚本\nforecast=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/Linhai?0\" | grep -v \"Follow\" | grep -v \"Location:\" | sed 's/\\x1b\\[[0-9;]*[a-zA-Z]//g')\nlocation=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/Linhai?format=%l\" | sed 's/\\x1b\\[[0-9;]*[a-zA-Z]//g')\n\n# 发送到当前飞书群\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw sessions send --session-key \"chat:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\" --message \"📅 台州临海天气预报提醒：\n地点：$location\n\n今日天气：\n$forecast\"\n"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775732651746,"responseId":"0217757326501074bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f9dbc12a"}}
